<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehst etliche schrift der
                                <expan>abschaidu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> von Ulme
                                <expan>schikt<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., also
                            <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir uns <add>nu</add> mit
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etwas davon <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>reden</expan>,
                        und <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> wolgefallen und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewr <expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan>, daz ir ewr erber
                                <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
                        rate auf die <app><note><q type="date">mitwoch zu nacht nach
                            <expan>purificac<ex>i</ex>o<ex>n</ex>is</expan> Marie schierist</q>03.02.1423</note></app> zu uns
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> schiket, von den wir etwas
                                <expan>ewer<ex>er</ex></expan> meynung und sie <add>auch</add> etwas
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vernemen mugen. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>conv<ex>er</ex>sion<ex>is</ex></expan> Pauli. </ab>
</div>
